quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,50,"Vachati: “Vatumwa venyu havana kuuya kwamuri here nezviratidzo zviri pachena here?” Vachati: “Hongu.” Vachava vanopindura: “Shevedzai sekuda kwenyu! Uye chikumbiro chevasingatendi hachina basa (chakarasika) (nekuti Allah havachitambiri)!”"
  40,51,"Zvirokwazvo, tichava tinoita kuti vatumwa vedu neavo vanotenda (muhumwechete waAllah) vave vakabudirira muhupenyu hwepano pasi uye muzuva iro vapupuri vachava vanomira (vachipupura pazuva rekutongwa)"
  40,52,"Zuva iro vanoita mabasa akaipa zvichemo zvavo zvichange zvisingabatsiri. Kurengera (kutukwa) kuchange kuri kwavari, uye nzvimbo yakaipa ichange iri yavo"
  40,53,Uye zvirokwazvo takave tinopa Musa nungamiri uye takave tinogadza Gwaro (Torah) senhaka kuvana vaIzrairi
  40,54,Nungamiri uye yeuchidzo kuvanhu vanonzwisisa
  40,55,"Naizvozvo iva unotsungirira (Muhammad (SAW)). Zvirokwazvo, vimbiso yaAllah ndeye chokwadi, uye kumbira ruregerero kubva kuzvitadzo zvako, wova unorumbidza rukudzo rwaTenzi vako munguva dzemasikati (kusvikira zuva radoka) uye munguva dzemangwanani (Hanzi zvichireva minamato mishanu pazuva kana kuti Asr neFajr)"
  40,56,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanopikisa pamusoro pezviratidzo zvaAllah vasina mvumo yauya kwavari, havana chimwe chinhu kusara kwekuzvitutumadza mumoyo yavo. Havasi kuzochiwana (chiporofita chawapihwa naAllah). Naizvozvo kumbira chengetedzo kuna Allah. Muzvirokwazvo, ndivo munzwi wezvose, muoni wezvose"
  40,57,"Zvirokwazvo, kusikwa kwedenga nenyika kukuru kukunda kusikwa kwevanhu, asi vanhu vazhinji havazvizive"
  40,58,"Uye havana kufanana avo vanoona neavo vasingaoni, kana avo vanotenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah) vachiita mabasa akanaka, neavo vanoita mabasa akaipa. Zvishoma ndizvo zvamunoyeuka"